#: data/cargo-write.desktop.in:5
msgid "Cargo Write"
msgstr "Cargo Write"

#: data/cargo-write.desktop.in:6 data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:43
msgid "Sticky notes"
msgstr "Klisterlappar"

#: data/cargo-write.desktop.in:7
msgid ""
"Write down notes, reminders, random thoughts and other short-term "
"informations"
msgstr ""
"Skriv ner anteckningar, påminnelser, slumpmässiga tankar och annan kortvarig "
"information"

#: data/cargo-write.desktop.in:13
msgid "text;plain;plaintext;notepad;notes;sticky;post-it;"
msgstr ""
"text;vanlig;vanlig text;anteckningsblock;anteckningar;klisterlappar;post-it;"

#: data/cargo-write.desktop.in:18
msgid "New sticky note"
msgstr "Ny klisterlapp"

#: data/cargo-write.desktop.in:23
msgid "Show Preferences"
msgstr "Visa inställningar"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:8
msgid "Write on colourful little squares"
msgstr "Skriv på färgglada små rutor"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:11
msgid "Features include:"
msgstr "Funktioner inkluderar:"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:13
msgid "Colourful: Ten pretty themes. Any new note gets a random one"
msgstr ""
"Färgglad: Tio vackra teman. Varje ny anteckning får ett slumpmässigt tema"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:14
msgid "Adaptive: New notes get the zoom you last chose"
msgstr "Anpassningsbar: Nya anteckningar får den zoomning du senast valde"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:15
msgid "Cute: Each new note has a funny or cute random (editable) title"
msgstr ""
"Söt: Varje ny anteckning har en rolig eller söt slumpmässig (redigerbar) "
"titel"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:16
msgid "Handy: You can open links and emails with Ctrl+Click"
msgstr "Praktiskt: Du kan öppna länkar och e-postmeddelanden med Ctrl+klick"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:17
msgid "Private: Try the scribble mode!"
msgstr "Privat: Prova klotterläget!"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:19
msgid ""
"This is a fork of an old version of \"Notejot\" by lainsce. The community "
"liked it so much, we thought it would be great to revive it!"
msgstr ""
"Detta är en förgrening av en gammal version av \"Notejot\" av lainsce. "
"Gemenskapen gillade den så mycket att vi tyckte det skulle vara fantastiskt "
"att återuppliva den!"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:27
msgid "Lainsce + Stella"
msgstr "Lainsce + Stella"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:44
msgid "Sticky note"
msgstr "Klisterlapp"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:45
msgid "Stickies"
msgstr "Klisterlappar"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:46
msgid "Colourful"
msgstr "Färgglad"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:47
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "Anteckningar"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:48
msgid "Cute"
msgstr "Söt"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:49
msgid "Desktop"
msgstr "Skrivbord"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:50
msgid "Reminder"
msgstr "Påminnelse"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:51
msgid "Utility"
msgstr "Verktyg"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:52
msgid "Pantheon"
msgstr "Pantheon"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:53
msgid "elementary OS"
msgstr "elementary OS"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:71
msgid "A sticky note with the \"Blueberry\" theme"
msgstr "En klisterlapp med temat \"Blåbär\""

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:75
msgid ""
"Streaming? Worried of someone looking above your shoulder? Try the scribbly "
"Mode!"
msgstr ""
"Strömning? Oroar du dig för att någon ska kika över din axel? Prova "
"kladdläget!"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:79
msgid "Look! Ascii art in a sticky note!"
msgstr "Titta! Ascii-konst på en klisterlapp!"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:83
msgid "The preferences dialog in light mode"
msgstr "Inställningsdialogen i ljust läge"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:87
msgid "The preferences dialog in dark mode"
msgstr "Inställningsdialogen i mörkt läge"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:95
msgid "🚀 4.0.0 Launch Update"
msgstr "🚀 4.0.0 Cargo Write of Hyperspace!"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:97
msgid "Version 4 to align with Gtk version"
msgstr "Version 4 för att anpassa till Gtk-versionen"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:98
msgid "Added button to toggle lists, and ability to customize them"
msgstr ""
"Lagt till knapp för att växla mellan listor och möjlighet att anpassa dem"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:99
msgid "Ctrl+Scroll to zoom-in, zoom-out"
msgstr "Ctrl+rulla för att zooma in, zooma ut"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:100
msgid "More zoom options"
msgstr "Flera zoomalternativ"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:101
msgid "Keyboard shortcuts work from popover now"
msgstr "Tangentbordsgenvägar fungerar nu från popover"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:102
msgid "A couple visual bugfixes as well!"
msgstr "Några visuella buggfixar också!"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:103
msgid "Various under the hood performance improvements"
msgstr "Olika prestandaförbättringar under huven"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:105 data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:140
#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:180
msgid "😎 Guests stars:"
msgstr "😎 Gäststjärnor:"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:107
msgid "Updated JA translation thanks to @ryonakano!"
msgstr "Uppdaterad JA-översättning tack vare @ryonakano!"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:108
msgid "You, the user, for liking this lil app!"
msgstr "Du, användaren, för att du gillar den här lilla appen!"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:120
msgid "Added windows build. It doesnt need admin rights. Mostly works."
msgstr ""
"Windows-version tillagd. Kräver inte administratörsrättigheter. Fungerar i "
"stort sett."

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:125
msgid "No fun allowed: revert back to default style"
msgstr "Inget skoj tillåtet: återgå till standardstil"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:130
msgid "🕷️ 3.4.0 Autumn Update"
msgstr "🕷️ 3.4.0 Autumn Update of Boo"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:132
msgid "Some UI elements show up after being shown, for a sleek vibe"
msgstr ""
"Vissa gränssnittselement visas efter att de har visats, för en elegant känsla"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:133
msgid "Ctrl+L to focus note title"
msgstr "Ctrl+L för att markera anteckningens titel"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:134
msgid "Ctrl+G (For Gear) or Ctrl+O (for Open) to open note settings now"
msgstr ""
"Ctrl+G (för Gear) eller Ctrl+O (för Open) för att öppna "
"anteckningsinställningarna nu"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:135
msgid "Alt+Number to change theme quickly"
msgstr "Alt+nummer för att snabbt ändra tema"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:136
msgid ""
"New note setting: Monospace (Ctrl+M). Could be for accessibility, could be "
"for ascii doodles"
msgstr ""
"Ny anteckningsinställning: Monospace (Ctrl+M). Kan vara som hjälpmedel, kan "
"vara för ascii-klotter"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:137
msgid ""
"Cleaner, nicer code under the hood. Probably marginally enhanced "
"performances or less edge bugs"
msgstr ""
"Renare, snyggare kod under huven. Förmodligen marginellt förbättrad "
"prestanda eller färre buggar"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:138
msgid "Added a reset-settings commandline option. Could be handy."
msgstr ""
"Lagt till en kommandoradsflagga för återställning av inställningar. Kan vara "
"praktiskt."

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:142
msgid "@wpkelso strikes again with an amazing special edition icon!"
msgstr "@wpkelso slår till igen med en fantastisk specialutgåva av ikonen!"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:149
msgid ""
"Bugfix: Fix Cargo Write lingering in the background not opening anymore if "
"all windows were closed (#77)"
msgstr ""
"Buggfix: Fixar att Cargo Write som kvarstår i bakgrunden inte längre öppnas "
"om alla fönster stängts (#77)"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:155
msgid "3.3.0 Interface Update"
msgstr "3.3.0 Interface Update"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:157
msgid ""
"Bugfix: Whole window being grabbable interfered with text editing. Only "
"actionbar and header are, now (#75, #76)"
msgstr ""
"Buggfix: Hela fönstret kunde dras, vilket störde textredigeringen. Nu är det "
"bara åtgärdsfältet och rubriken som kan dras (#75, #76)."

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:158
msgid "Added more random titles"
msgstr "Lade till fler slumpmässiga titlar"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:159
msgid "Buttons for add/remove autostart"
msgstr "Knappar för att lägga till/ta bort autostart"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:160
msgid "Some more title placeholders"
msgstr "Några fler platshållare för titlar"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:161
msgid "Under the hood is a bit cleaner now"
msgstr "Under huven är det lite renare nu"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:167
msgid ""
"Bugfix: When toggled off, the actionbar would leave an empty space. It is "
"now fixed - With now a flashier animation to boot."
msgstr ""
"Buggfix: När funktionen var avstängd lämnade åtgärdsfältet ett tomt utrymme. "
"Detta är nu fixat – och dessutom med en flashigare animation."

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:172
msgid "🌈 3.2.0 Pride Update"
msgstr "🌈 3.2.0 Pride Update"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:174
msgid "Add a cool little animation when enabling/disabling actionbar"
msgstr ""
"Lägg till en cool liten animation när du aktiverar/inaktiverar åtgärdsfältet"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:175
msgid "Fixed blurrinness in high-scaled display"
msgstr "Fixat suddighet vid högupplöst visning"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:176
msgid "Added high-resolution screenshots"
msgstr "Lagt till högupplösta skärmdumpar"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:177
msgid ""
"Last minute bugfix, somehow accels did not work when the Preferences were "
"focused"
msgstr ""
"Sista minuten-bugfix, av någon anledning fungerade inte snabbtangenter när "
"inställningarna var i fokus"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:178
msgid "A bit of housekeeping for FR and DE while at it"
msgstr "Lite städning för FR och DE medan vi ändå håller på"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:182
msgid "A lovely temporary icon by @wpkelso"
msgstr "En fin temporärikon av @wpkelso"

#: data/cargo-write.metainfo.xml.in:183
msgid "Updated EL translations thanks to @OrionasKakomoiroglou!"
msgstr "Uppdaterade EL-översättningar tack vare @OrionasKakomoiroglou!"

#~ msgid "Change colours, zoom in and out, and there is even an emoji button!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ändra färg, zooma in och ut, och det finns till och med en emoji-knapp!"
